comment:
This video features interviews with students from Kyunghee University about their favorite binge-watching series on Netflix. In addition to discussing their favorite shows, each interviewee is asked what they would say if they had the chance to meet the CEO of Netflix. 

The video also acknowledges Netflix's recent announcement about reducing subscription fees for users who agree to watch commercial ads. 
Overall, the video offers insights into the impact of binge-watching on viewing habits and the evolving streaming services industry.

짝짝짝~~ 다큐멘터리 작품으로 손색이 없구~ 넷플릭스 about 시리즈 콘텐츠 계속 계속 제작해도 좋을것 같아요. 러닝타임은 짧게. 예상외 얼렁뚱딴 인터뷰 답변들이 더 많이 나와도 참 재밌을것 겉아요. 짝짝짝.  글구 러시아 vs 우크라이나 학생들 편을 숏 필름으로 구성해 콘텐츠 해도 좋을것 같아요. 믿고 보는 탠씨TV 콘텐츠 great ^^
